{"tid":2358082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒：特朗普考慮自我特赦","createTime":"2021-01-08T01:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T07:17:52.000Z","uid":212249,"like":139,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"8812bc91c65768605d720505c48f4435ca637428","tid":2358082,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國傳媒報道，自去年11月大選以來，總統特朗普一直與幕僚討論考慮特赦自己。 <br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》引述兩名知情人士指，自從去年11月大選以來，特朗普數次與幕僚討論，考慮運用總統的特赦權力特赦自己，又曾詢問幕僚是否應該這麼做，以及在法律和政治上對他有何影響。不過報道指，未知特朗普在發生支持者強行闖入國會大樓後，是否還有討論此事。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾於2018年在社交平台發文指，他有「絕對權利」特赦自己，但總統特赦僅限於聯邦罪行，無法阻止特朗普正面臨紐約等地方檢察官對他的刑事和民事調查。有憲法律師指，對於總統能否合法特赦自己，沒有確實答案，過往也未曾有總統這麼做。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普的總統任期將於本月20日屆滿，白宮暫時未回應事件。"},{"pid":"059df10371459544b5ae1c79927dd0e9c75de758","tid":2358082,"uid":212249,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T01:24:34.000Z","msg":"美媒：特朗普考慮自我特赦<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=419469&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419469%26refer%3DShare&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=708bb02b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D419469%26refer%3DShare&h=7726fedc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=419469&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"ae5903b7a20141479724f76828b61d49a7ec6bb0","tid":2358082,"uid":127575,"like":117,"dislike":2,"score":115,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T01:26:23.000Z","msg":"就算拜登特赦佢<br />\n左膠一定要求拜登同民主黨趕盡殺絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5fd93f275cd14cb6af468ac0102989e469ca30","tid":2358082,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T01:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla